(77, 1, '2017-07-19 03:58:00', '2017-07-19 03:58:00', 'The collaboration between The Ordinary Co and Clinique is the most anticipated collection of accessories not to be missed! <a href=\"http://theordinary.co/\">The Ordinary Co</a> was founded in 2014 by their founder, Monica Lie. Reviewing from their past collections, they have never failed to provide exquisite and sophisticated pieces. The Ordinary Co will be releasing 16 new designs inspired by Clinique’s latest launched product,  <em><a href=\"http://www.clinique.com.sg/products/8388/skin-care/hydration\">Moisture Surge™ Hydrating Supercharged Concentrate</a></em> this Mothers’ Day. The essence of the pink tones and swirling bubbles in the bottle majorly influenced the latest collection featuring hues of pink in the design. Here at Foxesden, we were lucky enough to have a first hand look and find out what the collection has to offer!\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_84\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/collab.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-84 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/collab.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Dainty, intricate and timeless. The 3 perfect words to describe their latest collection.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/necklace-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-83 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/necklace-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_82\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"675\"]<a data-size=\"675x900\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Portrait-Guide.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-82 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Portrait-Guide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"675\" height=\"900\" /></a> Our favourite piece throughout the collection! Extremely eye catching and a stunning piece. The subtle pink hues adds a lovely vibe and the structure of the bangle creates a classy and sophisticated image.[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_81\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/necklace.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-81 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/necklace.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> This layered necklace is definitely a versatile and a ‘to go for’ piece, styled for any occasion, to bring the outfit from casual to chic.[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_80\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/pair.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-80 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/pair.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Another impressive collection indeed! The best part is that nothing is over $30 in this collection. Just like their business philosophy, inspire every girl to make accessorising part of her every day life with simple and affordable pieces.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mother.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-79 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mother.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/family.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-78 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/family.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Ordinary Co has also recently posted their new collection pictures on Lookbook in view of Mothers’ Day. Simple and lightweight yet elegant and fashionable. If you have yet to prepare a gift for your mother, head over to <a href=\"http://theordinary.co/\">The Ordinary Co</a> and shop for her timeless pieces. And a special treat for our readers! All Foxesden readers are entitled to a 10% discount (*T&amp;C applied) when you spend a minimum amount of $30 on their online site. Just type the promocode FOXESDENxTOC at the payment page. Hurry make your purchases now as the code expires on 30 June 2017.\r\n<div><em>*T&amp;Cs: Applies to all items at <a href=\"http://www.theordinary.co/\">www.theOrdinary.co</a> except Custom jewelry and Sensitive Ears. </em><em>Items purchased with discount are not exchangeable except for defects. Discount does not include shipping. Expires on 30 June 2017.</em></div>', 'Clinique x Ordinary Co', 'The Ordinary Co will be releasing 16 new designs inspired by Clinique’s latest launched product,  Moisture Surge™ Hydrating Supercharged Concentrate this Mothers’ Day.', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'clinique-x-ordinary-co', '', '', '2017-07-20 05:07:33', '2017-07-20 05:07:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/foxesden/?post_type=beauty&#038;p=77', 0, 'beauty-post', '', 0),
