(87, 1, '2017-07-19 04:55:38', '2017-07-19 04:55:38', '<h2>Are You a Fan of Denim?</h2>\r\nAre you a denim lover? If yes, how much? If you look through the history of fashion, denim has always been involved somehow. It is one of the most functional fabrics and you don’t have to be a super model to pull it off! We have gathered a number of sets featuring stunning denim fashion trends for 2017. Lets jump-start the new month with a new wardrobe!\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_95\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"768\"]<img class=\"wp-image-95 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/hbz-denim-gigi-hadid-splash-768x1152.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" /> Gigi Hadid wearing Parker Smith Bombshell Bell in thunderstorm, SGD250[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_94\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"768\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-94\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/romee-strijd-in-denim-dress-shopping-at-house-of-cb-in-west-hollywood-06-10-2016_13-768x1152.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" /> Romee Strijd in Denim Button-front Midi Dress from Made well, SGD 200. The dutch model from Victoria Secret matched the dress with a navy blue bandana scarf.[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_93\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"236\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-93\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/020fd8d14d2343c333d69deb5e218794-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"236\" height=\"697\" /> Below the knee skirts are definitely the newest trend! It is elegant, soothing out lines, accentuating all the places that should be shown off. However, the secret to pulling off the longer skirt is to wear for you height. If you prefer something shorter, you may look out for something similar to this.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-92\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/9d147ecd6657012852e67660bfa71f8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-91\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/gallery-1462914653-hbz-florence-welch.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"720\" />\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_90\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"974\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-90\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/customised_WW_test-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"974\" height=\"556\" /> Even the popular online shop ASOS also released a whole new season focus mainly on patched and unique ripped denim jeans. The best part is that you can get most of them under SGD 100![/caption]\r\n<h3 class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">There is a saying that says “A good pair of jean can last you a life time”.</h3>\r\n<p class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">If you are like me being completely in love of silken blouse then you will understand how hard it is to find something that can match with it. Since the silken material is shinny, you will need something rough and dull to contrast it. Therefore, denim jeans will be the ultimate match.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">Tips</h3>\r\n<p class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">Sadly Denim age with every wash and wear. Here are some tips on how you can take care of your jeans by <a href=\"http://parkersmith.com/denim-care/\">Parker Smith</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wash jeans before first wear</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash with similar colour in the same load to prevent fading</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash with cold water</li>\r\n 	<li>To prevent shrinkage and maintain its original shape, you should limit the amount of washes between wears.</li>\r\n 	<li>Alter your jeans based your specific height and inseam to achieve the best look.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Latest Denim Trends for 2017!', 'It is one of the most functional fabrics and you don’t have to be a super model to pull it off!', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'latest-denim-trends-for-2017', '', '', '2017-07-26 09:34:16', '2017-07-26 09:34:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/foxesden/?post_type=fashion&#038;p=87', 0, 'fashion-post', '', 0),
(88, 1, '2017-07-11 09:03:38', '2017-07-11 09:03:38', '<h2>Are You a Fan of Denim?</h2>\r\nAre you a denim lover? If yes, how much? If you look through the history of fashion, denim has always been involved somehow. It is one of the most functional fabrics and you don’t have to be a super model to pull it off! We have gathered a number of sets featuring stunning denim fashion trends for 2017. Lets jump-start the new month with a new wardrobe!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">There is a saying that says “A good pair of jean can last you a life time”.</h3>\r\n<p class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">If you are like me being completely in love of silken blouse then you will understand how hard it is to find something that can match with it. Since the silken material is shinny, you will need something rough and dull to contrast it. Therefore, denim jeans will be the ultimate match.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">Tips</h3>\r\n<p class=\"article-content--title\" data-reactid=\"96\">Sadly Denim age with every wash and wear. Here are some tips on how you can take care of your jeans by <a href=\"http://parkersmith.com/denim-care/\">Parker Smith</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wash jeans before first wear</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash with similar colour in the same load to prevent fading</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash with cold water</li>\r\n 	<li>To prevent shrinkage and maintain its original shape, you should limit the amount of washes between wears.</li>\r\n 	<li>Alter your jeans based your specific height and inseam to achieve the best look.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Latest Denim Trends for 2017!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-11 09:03:38', '2017-07-11 09:03:38', '', 87, 'http://localhost:8888/foxesden/87-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
