(99, 1, '2017-07-11 09:06:42', '2017-07-11 09:06:42', 'The collaboration between The Ordinary Co and Clinique is the most anticipated collection of accessories not to be missed! <a href=\"http://theordinary.co/\">The Ordinary Co</a> was founded in 2014 by their founder, Monica Lie. Reviewing from their past collections, they have never failed to provide exquisite and sophisticated pieces. The Ordinary Co will be releasing 16 new designs inspired by Clinique’s latest launched product,  <em><a href=\"http://www.clinique.com.sg/products/8388/skin-care/hydration\">Moisture Surge™ Hydrating Supercharged Concentrate</a></em> this Mothers’ Day. The essence of the pink tones and swirling bubbles in the bottle majorly influenced the latest collection featuring hues of pink in the design. Here at Foxesden, we were lucky enough to have a first hand look and find out what the collection has to offer!\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13E0p_NxsuU\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_84\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<img class=\"wp-image-84 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/collab.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /> Dainty, intricate and timeless. The 3 perfect words to describe their latest collection.[/caption]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-83\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/necklace-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" />\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_82\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"675\"]<img class=\"wp-image-82 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Portrait-Guide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"675\" height=\"900\" /> Our favourite piece throughout the collection! Extremely eye catching and a stunning piece. The subtle pink hues adds a lovely vibe and the structure of the bangle creates a classy and sophisticated image.[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_81\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<img cl