(164, 1, '2017-07-19 04:56:31', '2017-07-19 04:56:31', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-171\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/810.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"c-figure__title\">Cara Delevingne</h2>\r\nCara Delevingne shaved her head for her role as a cancer patient in <em>Life in a Year</em>, but embraced her new crop by dyeing it platinum blonde.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/810-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"c-figure__title\">Natalie Portman</h2>\r\nProof that with a face that pretty you can get away with any hairstyle, Natalie Portman stole the show at the Cannes Film Festival in 2005 with her ultra-short look, having shaved it for her role in <em>V For Vendetta</em>. Luminous, as ever.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/810-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"c-figure__title\">Grace Bol</h2>\r\nWith her close-cropped hair and statuesque presence - she\'s just under six feet tall - Sudanese model Grace Bol has walked for the likes of Balmain, Emilio Pucci and Marc Jacobs, as well as starring in beauty campaigns for Nars, MAC and Sephora.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-167\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/810-4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" />\r\n<h2 class=\"c-figure__title\">Sinéad O\'Connor</h2>\r\nThink of the Prince-penned track <em>Nothing Compares 2 U</em> and it\'s impossible not to immediately picture Irish singer-songwriter Sinéad O\'Connor in the song\'s iconic video - huge doe eyes, raw emotion and perhaps the most memorable buzz cut of all time.\r\n<h6>GETTY IMAGES</h6>', 'Best Buzz Cuts', 'Would you shave your head? These stars did, and looked all the more beautiful because of it.', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'best-buzz-cuts', '', '', '2017-07-20 05:07:30', '2017-07-20 05:07:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/foxesden/?post_type=beauty-post&#038;p=164', 0, 'beauty-post', '', 0),
