(264, 1, '2017-07-26 08:40:36', '2017-07-26 08:40:36', 'What time is it? Summer time!!! That’s right, sun’s out, so it’s perfectly justified for us to show some skin and chill by the pool. While bikinis might have been every girl’s go-to in these hot summer months, one-piece swimsuits are making a comeback. With many celebrities and models (e.g. Gigi Hadid and Kendall Jenner) rocking swimsuits during their vacations, it’s proving to be a must-have item of the season.\r\n\r\nSwimsuits are reportedly flattering for every body type due to its high-cut, leg-baring style. The style gives an illusion of having an elongated body and long legs, while cinching in at the waist to show off a small waistline.\r\n\r\nWe’ve put together a curation of different swimsuits to help everyone find their perfect fit and design, so continue scrolling to see more!\r\n<h2>Fun and Quirky</h2>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_265\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-265 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Left: <a href=\"http://www.forever21.com/Product/Product.aspx?BR=F21&amp;Category=swimwear_one-piece&amp;ProductID=2000134015&amp;VariantID=013\">Unique Vintage One-Piece Swimsuit</a> | Right: <a href=\"http://www.asos.com/asos/asos-80s-sprinkles-print-swimsuit/prd/8091037?iid=8091037&amp;clr=80sgraphic&amp;SearchQuery=&amp;cid=10118&amp;pgesize=36&amp;pge=0&amp;totalstyles=514&amp;gridsize=3&amp;gridrow=1&amp;gridcolumn=3\">ASOS 80s Sprinkles Print Swimsuit</a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nSummer’s all about bright, shocking colours, so don’t be afraid to make a statement with your most loud and popping swimsuit! Perfect for poolside parties or a gathering with your girlfriends, these one-pieces allow you to remain cool while looking as cute as a button.\r\n<h2>Athletic Vibes</h2>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_269\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-269 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Left: Body Glove Rocky Swimsuit | Right: RVCA Rib Swimsuit[/caption]\r\n\r\nFor all you sporty girls out there who aren’t interested in looking too girly and made-up, this one’s for you! The outer-edge piping and two-toned muted shades on these swimsuits contribute to giving it an athletic vibe, creating an edgy and effortless look.\r\n<h2>Tropical Florals</h2>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_268\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-268 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Left: Off-the-shoulder Swimsuit | Right: ASOS Midnight Floral Lace Trim Plunge Swimsuit[/caption]\r\n\r\nClearly we can’t live without florals during the warmer months, and this is no exception for swimsuits. Consider rocking these tropical numbers, either in an off-the-shoulder cut, or with a plunging neckline to show off your sexy side.\r\n<h2>Conservative, but not boring</h2>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_267\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-267 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Left: High Neck Mesh Swimsuit | Right: Fuller Bust Swimsuit by Wolf &amp; Whistle[/caption]\r\n\r\nWant to remain modest and not show too much skin? These swimsuits basically scream “business in the front, party in the back”! Monochromatic with slight twists to its designs, the look remains conservative yet interesting at the same time.\r\n<h2>Retro Vintage</h2>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_266\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1024\"]<a data-size=\"1024x640\" href=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits6.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-266 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/foxesden/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/swimsuits6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" /></a> Left: Coastline Icon One-Piece Swimsuit | Right: Vera Moda Twist Front Bandeau Gingham Swimsuit[/caption]\r\n\r\nThrow it back to the 50s with these vintage inspired looks. Complete with halter necks and gingham prints, these one-piece swimsuits will help you to channel your inner pin-up girl as you lounge by the pool.', 'Pack away your bikinis, swimsuits are back in!', 'While bikinis might have been every girl’s go-to in these hot summer months, one-piece swimsuits are making a comeback.', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'pack-away-your-bikinis-swimsuits-are-back-in', '', '', '2017-07-26 09:34:49', '2017-07-26 09:34:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/foxesden/?post_type=fashion-post&#038;p=264', 0, 'fashion-post', '', 0),
